      "title": "Postal services limited for three days due to fuel crisis",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Considering the current fuel shortage in the country, the Postal Department has decided to open post and sub post offices three days a week.",
        "They said the decision was taken considering the transport and traveling difficulties.",
        "Accordingly, the services by the main and sub offices will be available on Tuesday, Wednesday, and Thursday. (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)"
      ],
